But the most disastrous
fallout was in Syria,

00:45:19.860 --> 00:45:22.510
and the most disastrous
fallout was in Syria

00:45:22.510 --> 00:45:26.040
exemplifying what international
relations theorists

00:45:26.040 --> 00:45:30.020
referred to as the moral
hazard of intervention,

00:45:30.020 --> 00:45:32.563
and this is the moral
hazard of intervention.

00:45:33.560 --> 00:45:37.540
The idea is if people
think that if we revolt,

00:45:37.540 --> 00:45:40.000
somebody will intervene and help us,

00:45:40.000 --> 00:45:42.630
